Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.06,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,56,28,,{\an3\b0\fnArial Narrow\fscx94\bord0\fscy98\blur0.996}A study in srt by Perevodildo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani mo nai tadatada tsudzuku sora
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing is endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani hitotsu te ni todokanai yōna
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hi no biru no sukima kara mieta gaitō ni
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,600)}And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Comment: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{OP ED border}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Small Factor, Small Factor, Small Factor only! \NAt this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And this guy. \NHow is this guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out yourself now\N no technique can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya, I believe, \Nthe goddess of fortune has left your mortal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't see a single drum \Nwith "seven" on it from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What I do is opposite - I attract Lady Luck. \NI'm her favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:02:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go. \NIf you excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But before I leave, \NI will say just one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If the depths of the slotter's heart are weak, \Nhis game will be weak as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The last drum is still spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba... Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,10,,{\fade(1200,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.394\shad0.996\blur1.992\3c&H394057&\4c&H9FA9A9&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs44.813\fscx114\fscy92}Episode 1 \N{\fs100}Windmill
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,0)}And now, let me give the floor \Nto our weather forecast host.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:11.70,Song,,0,0,0,,Right! Thanks a lot, colleague! \NToday I have a bunch of good news for all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again... I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt we might hear something better today, \Nthan the fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:39.12,Song,,0,0,10,,{\fade(800,0)\an8}Publishing house "Spinning Gears"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, I understand that what I'm saying \Nmight sound empty to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but if writing articles takes you so long, \Nwhy not use a fax once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:05:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No word processor is needed. No PC is needed. \NJust send the article out and mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither a word processor nor a PC \Nare in my possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what I'm saying. \NYou won't need any of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's whatcha mean... \NDoes it really bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You better listen to boss this time. We don't look forward to working till the last minute here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We should budget a fax for you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what a poor handwriting you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be more self-confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a single subject \Nthat is out of Ginya's competence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The audience loves him too.\NRight, Kawato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Can't argue with Amy here. \NFan mail is usually torn apart after his writings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, an article written by an aspiring novelist \Nremains a novel anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't call it high-quality journalism. \NBut the housewives seem to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How long in the faculty of literature again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years, then I graduated myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not familiar with the tabloid-style...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have some ideas of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I say OK. We're publishing this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't you be so kind \Nto pay me in advance for the next article?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Again and again, \Nyou ask for it every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more important, the next article will be \Nan unusual one. Come a little closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard one spicy conversation the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, in Japan, there's a place \Nwhere the best national slotters gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To determine the Number One among them, \Nthey play against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, maybe it's just a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want me to find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Or prove it doesn't exist... \NStill, at least half of this story is positively true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather try to find it and write about it? \NWe compensate any expenses you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm in trouble. Just what have I got involved in? \NA minute out of the office, and I'm lost already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That short old man might help me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't care less about my coffee. \NYou can only come here to see her, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think so? \NIt's not like that at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To get master's coffee, \NI'm ready to drive through the whole city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"For the coffee," he says! What an insolent fellow. \NHave you no honor at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you had breakfast? \NWhen was the last time you ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At five... PM yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What else did I expect... \NYou always forget basic things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your job these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little by little,{\i0} he says...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck with it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot, right? But what a pain... Why is it me who has to mess around with pachislot, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\NWorking hard already, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! With my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A free gift from a local supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A windmill, huh...\NBrings memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, brother, where does the wind come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,From the mountains? \NFrom the sea? From the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,From everywhere. \NBut what matters, Mai, is where it starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it is blowing straight out of our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straight from our hearts?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it makes the windmill spin? \NI wonder what color my heart prefers the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the color of the beautiful sky, blue? \NIs it the color of flowing clouds, white? Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bright red like a burning sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it bright red like a burning sunset...{\i0} Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, which color do you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What? \NYou can see the color while it's rotating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, this is the essential ingredient \Nof playing pachislot. Here. Your rice omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Essential ingredient?{\i0} \NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is holding your neck straight. \NThe essential ingredient is moving your eyes instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew you are also a pachislot Master. \NThat's yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of yummy, \Nthere's that one rumor I heard recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that there's a place \Nwhere the pachislot Number One is being determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know it, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate... But then, \Nwhat for do you have all these toys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Operational pachislot machines. In that kind of adult facility, they look a little out of place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure... you should write about pachislot \Nwith that kind of attitude towards it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my job, so I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Without experiencing the fun of playing it to the full, \Ncan you write a really high-grade article about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Impossible. \NI can't stop it in the right color.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya's eyesight is much more agile after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, I'll say the same thing I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you understand what is good and bad about this game, you won't write a comprehensive article.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, it's just better \Nto continue dreaming of becoming a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot might turn out to be a phenomenon \N you are unable to comprehend yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the point of saying this? I'm not the person \Nto teach you how to write. I believe it's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, young fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't, aging fellow.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was beyond your power after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:11:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep looking. This rumor couldn't have appeared out of nowhere. There is no smoke without fire, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no other assignments now anyway. \NContinue your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I did everything I could... \NMaybe I'm just too young to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not destined to ever see \Nthe battle for pachislot Number One title?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, if it really exists, \NI positively want to see it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try again! \NWhere there's a will there's a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I survive till the paycheck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead end. In a week or two, \Nfinding something except dead ends is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never too late to give everything up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But think about it yourself, \Nall cats are gray in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when they exist in rumors only...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the places I've been to \Nseemed to be even close to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To the place you are looking for. "Slothium."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slothium?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! You knew it after all! So unfair of you! \NAnd I was wondering why you look so smug lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium is a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where slotters who dream of becoming Number One \Ncompete against each other fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who succeed become pachislot aristocrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you who dreams of becoming a novelist, \Nwill hardly ever understand such an inferior dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those childish guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pachislot aristocracy fellows...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To understand them, one needs a heart. \NKeep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, no wonder this society is semi-secret. \NEven close friends are treated coldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes perfect sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Shibaura Futoshi, \Nwe are glad to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm bringing with me one guest \Nwilling to watch the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Name please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the monitor presented \Nto type in your name, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otonashi Ginya, your registration is now complete. \NPlease proceed to the main floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What it this facility? \NSome kind of underground villain base?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One hell of a luxury club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they do stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the game is on, on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your member card. \NSit wherever you like and make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. But I'd rather go see it from inside. \NFrom inside, you can see things a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon, dear guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have to wait for the next match, \Nstarting in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, fine. \NI just stopped by to see it in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Wait... Wait, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this fellow doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen this man before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What brought him there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he own a registration card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A minute into, \Nyou are already the center of attention, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,First one stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit distracting me! \NHow did you get here, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have intruded on our battlefield! \NIt's no place for wandering kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wandering?{\i0} \NWell... I said sorry, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,People here are too serious about the game after all... \NEven though I apologized, some are still mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, will ya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are this guy's intentions in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell you've done this for!? \NListen here, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have invaded the sacred place where we dream and live!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize right this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't thrown a coin at me, \NI might have agreed to make an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But not now, \Nwhen you've already made your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know one's fate may be decided \Nby a single coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But your deeds now \Nare not suitable for a real dreamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,People who dream of becoming Japan's number one slotter are bound to be gifted with some nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was hoping to see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only met a bunch of inept pseudo-dreamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I couldn't find a single adult \Nwho'd be worthy both in this game and in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You think this is just an unsophisticated game? \NWhy don't you try it yourself then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our system has your name registered \Nas a game member, not a spectator...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Each machine in Slothium is regularly serviced \Nso you can choose freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This particular game has started \Nwith a hundred coins on each score.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one to score two thousand points \Nis declared the game's winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a kid. Kids are always cheeky at first, \Nbut I'm used to shutting them up with one "Big."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can even allow you to start with about 370 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. \NLet's give him the idea once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You say the way we play for the dream is wrong. \NLet us see the right way then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how will the young blood act now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He accepted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I am interested too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The young man looks reckless, \Nbut will he also be prompt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Any ideas about what method is he planning to use?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I like him! \NCan I still change my bet to the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,New faces are present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba... Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He is about to be silenced for good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make this pretender of a man understand \Nthat Slothium does not tolerate the light-headed play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a defeat will make the best teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it happen? 4 left?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the boy's first game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I reckon you regret changing the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he not give up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He is done for, that's a plain truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Red, red, red, red...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one... \NA final Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still trying! \NIs he really that thickheaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll never find out who he is. \NYoung men are so unreliable these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't make it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ginya's eyes are so much more agile than mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it bright red like a sunset?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one last chance left...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,On this windmill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I place the bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Red... Red...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Red!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From such a situation, \Nyou could find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However, will your luck continue \Nto help you out like this in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A series! Renchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But how? \NWas he able to handle the Big too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why it's "Bar!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I got "Big!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over... Though, to be honest, \NI was already feeling my ass fried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The game is concluded. \NThis game's winner is Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,2000)}The final score is 2035...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember this name for now.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,5,,Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.22,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,800)}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,800)}Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miraculous technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \NFinger of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will \Nstop the time.
